{"tid":491474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔發惡】準備北韓人湧入 傳吉林邊境設5個難民營","createTime":"2017-12-06T14:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T18:19:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f948289c7957d251a8fd45aa177e437e5edae132","tid":491474,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512559061_2ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512559061_2ce0.jpg&h=28898682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮半島局勢緊張，瀕臨開戰邊緣，日媒更稱美國可能在本月18日對北韓開戰。中方亦開始做準備，除吉林省委今日在機關報上，刊登防核知識，網上今晚廣傳，一份負責內地通訊的中國移動集團亦發出內部通告，指一旦開戰，大批北韓民眾衝過國境，湧到中國，中國除在邊境設置多個難民營，並且已經派人到打算作為安置點的地點考察，安排移動通訊基站。<br />\n<br />\n這份文件是由「中移動集團吉林公司白山分公司長白分公司」發出，表明是「針對北韓難民安置點進行網絡覆蓋方案制定的請示」。文件指出，位於中朝邊境的吉林省長白縣政府稱，將會在當地設置5個難民安置點，安置地點包括長白沿江、長白十八道溝及長白雞冠砬子。<br />\n文件指出，長白分公司的經理付深海本月2日已經帶人到現場考察，及進行移動信號測試，發現其中兩個地點的信號覆蓋差，無法提供正常通訊，另一點則信號較弱。<br />\n長白縣有260公里的邊境，與北韓的兩江道惠山市、三池淵郡、普天郡、三水郡、金正淑郡、金亨稷郡等隔江相望，一旦北韓開戰，將是北韓民眾湧入的其中一個重災區。早前已預期一旦北韓開戰，將會數以十萬計難民湧到中國，解放軍亦一早調派軍隊，堵截難民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57549011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57549011&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5FdwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=af42cd6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57549011&h=061a899e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171206/57549011</a>"},{"pid":"fb9e8da6c315e739622f0f5bc57b004d0905f81a","tid":491474,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔：哦"},{"pid":"546064b42c92598dd928cfa48e53300fbc4ceb6c","tid":491474,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"吉林省gg, rip"},{"pid":"916d330d01e02349d830c35915c70c61fb6d3a04","tid":491474,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"港男唔港再忍受港女啦 <br />\n朝鮮妹係更好選擇<br />\n利申：ex係中國朝鮮族"},{"pid":"0f7e6968481b56e9cc143b66828757a4ce9385ab","tid":491474,"uid":11695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港男唔港再忍受港女啦 <br />\n朝鮮妹係更好選擇<br />\n利申：ex係中國朝鮮族</blockquote><br />\n屌屌下諗起成肚都係蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝鮮妹？不了。"},{"pid":"1787d743e36e4d9da60f3c1c7a4e482ec5df0571","tid":491474,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港男唔港再忍受港女啦 <br />\n朝鮮妹係更好選擇<br />\n利申：ex係中國朝鮮族</blockquote><br />\n屌屌下諗起成肚都係蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝鮮妹？不了。</blockquote><br />\n精蟲？"},{"pid":"a6e50f25ee35634f815a8a6e3e7bd5e7245454c3","tid":491474,"uid":3189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"北韓人 體內有勁多性病同寄生蟲<br />\n做性奴都唔得啦<br />\n拎去攪碎搾汁做肥料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca6bb3d9316450aeff58d65295a5b19ed07e336","tid":491474,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"c7313b226e9c803b7eb29f4af6ff58e12ee68f18","tid":491474,"uid":87511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"